casebody.data:
Monday, July 21, 1997

MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

97-1452. State ex rel. Rosenbaum v. Hanna.

This cause originated in this court on the filing of a complaint in prohibition. Upon consideration thereof,

IT IS ORDERED by the court, swa sponte, that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.

Douglas and F.E. Sweeney, JJ., dissent and would grant an alternative writ.
